data.description: Welcome to 26 Davis Ave, a timeless gem built in 1941 that seamlessly blends classic charm with modern comfort. This 4-bedroom, 1-1/2 bath residence boasts a thoughtful design, with the family room converted into a spacious master bedroom for added convenience. Spanning 1,726 square feet, the home sits on a generous .26-acre lot, providing a perfect balance of indoor and outdoor living. Enjoy the luxury of an attached two-car garage, ensuring hassle-free parking. The property features central air and heat, with the added benefit of dual systems, ensuring optimal comfort throughout. Rest easy knowing that major repairs are not a concern, and revel in the peace of mind provided by a new roof installed less than five years ago. Upstairs, a brand-new central air and heat system complements a recently renovated bathroom, while the kitchen, also less than five years old, showcases modern functionality.
